1. Lambda Expressions
----------------------
ex:-
(x, y) -> x + y  
void abstractFun(int x);//declaration in FuncInterface interface
FuncInterface fobj = (int x)->System.out.println(2*x);//obj creatin to interface and lambda expersion 
fobj.abstractFun(5);//calling

2. Functional Interfaces
-------------------------
Functional interfaces are also called Single Abstract Method interfaces (SAM Interfaces). As name suggest, a functional interface permits exactly one abstract method in it.

            


