=>stream API -new stream API to facilitate pipeline processing( the Stream API is used to process collections of objects. A stream is a sequence of objects that supports various methods which can be pipelined to produce the desired result. The features of Java stream are â€“ A stream is not a data structure instead it takes input from the Collections, Arrays or I/O channels.)
